```plantuml
@startuml Speccy-Rom_SpeccyTV
actor User

participant "movies_auth" as Auth
participant "movies_async_api" as AsyncAPI
participant "movies_billing" as Billing
participant "movies_streaming_converter" as Converter
participant "movies_streaming_etl" as ETL
participant "movies_admin" as Admin
participant "movies_streaming_admin" as StreamingAdmin
participant "movies_ugc" as UGC
participant "MinIO" as Storage
participant "Kafka" as Kafka
participant "ClickHouse" as ClickHouse
participant "Redis" as Redis
participant "Elasticsearch" as Elastic
participant "PostgreSQL" as PostgreSQL

User -> Auth: Authenticate (JWT/Google OAuth)
Auth -> AsyncAPI: Request movie data
AsyncAPI -> Elastic: Search movies
Elastic -> AsyncAPI: Return movie data
AsyncAPI -> User: Display movie data

User -> Billing: Subscribe (Stripe)
Billing -> PostgreSQL: Update subscription info
PostgreSQL -> Billing: Confirm subscription
Billing -> User: Subscription confirmed

User -> Converter: Convert video resolution
Converter -> MinIO: Fetch original video
MinIO -> Converter: Return video
Converter -> MinIO: Store converted video

ETL -> Converter: Trigger conversion task (via DAG)
ETL -> Storage: Manage video files
ETL -> StreamingAdmin: Update streaming metadata

User -> Admin: Manage content (Django UI)
Admin -> PostgreSQL: Update content info
PostgreSQL -> Admin: Confirm update
Admin -> User: Content updated

User -> UGC: Post user-generated content
UGC -> Kafka: Stream event
Kafka -> ClickHouse: Store event data
ClickHouse -> UGC: Confirm storage

@enduml
```